data.description:
Assumable loan available of $600,000 at 4.5%.  Buyer must qualify with Freedom Mortgage and be an owner occupant. 

Welcome to Trails at Crowfoot in Parker, where luxury and modern comfort meet in this stunning newly constructed home.  The bright and open floorpan seamlessly connects the living, dining and kitchen areas creating a perfect place for entertaining. The well appointed kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooktop w/hood, built-in oven, microwave and oversized kitchen island.  Enjoy hardwood flooring throughout the entire main level and an inviting floor to ceiling built-in fireplace in the living room.  The main level also offers a light filled office/den and powder bathroom. On the upper level you'll find three bedrooms and two bathrooms, including the main bedroom with an ensuite bathroom.  There is also additional open space for an small office/studio/play area.  The home is situated on a lot which backs to open space for nice views of the natural surroundings and increased privacy.  Enjoy oversized sliding glass doors which lead to a large patio and yard which is fully landscaped, irrigated and fenced! This home is move in ready!
